tables.name: students
tables.def:
CREATE TABLE students (
  student_id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY
  , student_name VARCHAR(64)
)

tables.name: teachers
tables.def:
CREATE TABLE teachers (
  teacher_id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY
  , teacher_name VARCHAR(64)
)

tables.name: courses

constraints.name: - (Foreign key ID: 0)
constraints.def: FOREIGN KEY (teacher_id) REFERENCES teachers (teacher_id) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION MATCH NONE

tables.def:
CREATE TABLE courses (
  course_id VARCHAR(16) PRIMARY KEY
  , course_name VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL
  , teacher_id BIGINT
  , FOREIGN KEY (teacher_id) REFERENCES teachers(teacher_id)
)

tables.name: student_courses

constraints.name: - (Foreign key ID: 0)
constraints.def: FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES students (student_id) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION MATCH NONE

constraints.name: - (Foreign key ID: 1)
constraints.def: FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses (course_id) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION MATCH NONE

tables.def:
CREATE TABLE student_courses (
  course_id VARCHAR(16)
  , student_id BIGINT

  , FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses(course_id)
  , FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES students(student_id)
  , PRIMARY KEY (course_id, student_id)
)

relations.def: FOREIGN KEY (teacher_id) REFERENCES teachers (teacher_id) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION MATCH NONE
FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES students (student_id) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION MATCH NONE
FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES courses (course_id) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION MATCH NONE
